Class Facility

java.lang.Object
assign02.Facility
public class Facility extends Object
This class represents a record of patients that have visited a UHealth facility. It maintains a collection of CurrentPatients.

    • lookupByPhysician

      public ArrayList<CurrentPatient> lookupByPhysician(int physician)
      Retrieves the patient(s) with the given physician.
      Parameters:

      Returns:
      a list of patient(s) with the given physician (in any order), or an empty list if no such patients exist in the record

    • getRecentPatients

      public ArrayList<CurrentPatient> getRecentPatients(GregorianCalendar date)
      Retrieves the patient(s) with last visits newer than a given date. Note that GregorianCalendar includes a compareTo method that may be useful. NOTE: If the last visit date equals this date, do not add the patient.
      Parameters:
      date - - cutoff date earlier than visit date of all returned patients
      Returns:
      a list of patient(s) with last visit date after cutoff (in any order), or an empty list if no such patients exist in the record

    • getPhysicianList

      public ArrayList<Integer> getPhysicianList()
      Retrieves a list of physicians assigned to patients at this facility. NOTE: Do not put duplicates in the list. Make sure each physician is only added once.
      Returns:
      a list of physician(s) assigned to current patients, or an empty list if no patients exist in the record

    • setPhysician

      public void setPhysician(UHealthID patientID, int physician)
      Sets the physician of a patient with the given UHealthID. NOTE: If no patient with the ID exists in the collection, then this method has no effect.
      Parameters:
      patientID - - UHealthID of patient to modify
      physician - - identifier of patient's new physician

    • setLastVisit

      public void setLastVisit(UHealthID patientID, GregorianCalendar date)
      Sets the last visit date of a patient with the given UHealthID. NOTE: If no patient with the ID exists in the collection, then this method has no effect.
      Parameters:
      patientID - - UHealthID of patient to modify
      date - - date of last visit
